===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[ordered]] [[pair]]''' (''plural'' '''ordered pairs''')

#{{settheory}} A [[set]] containing exactly two [[element]]s in a fixed order, so that, when the elements are different, exchanging them gives a different set.  Notation: (a, b) ''or'' <math>\langle a, b\rangle</math>

